Package engine.space

Classes for representing and manipulating multidimensional space.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ISpatialObject
    Represents an object that has some notion of space, and can be stored in a ISpatialStructure.
    ISpatialStructure<T extends ISpatialObject>
    A data structure that stores objects with a notion of space.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AABB
    A 3D axis-aligned bounding box.
    Grid<T extends ISpatialObject>
    Represents a 2D space with a grid
    QuadTree<T extends ISpatialObject>
    Represents a 2D space that can be recursively divided into 4 equal subspaces.
